FIG. 10 is a left side view of a third embodiment of the apparatus of FIG. 1 with the fertilizer weldment mounted to a bracket behind the shank to provide a uniform operating width at the operating level above the point;


FIG. 11 is a left side elevational view of a fourth embodiment of the invention in which the fertilizer weldment is adapted to an existing tillage shank; and


FIG. 12 is a rear view of the apparatus of FIG. 11.
